frontmatter.title: Changelogs
frontmatter.meta_title: ListPro - Listing Directory app by React native
frontmatter.meta_description: ListPro helps you to create, manage, organize and monetize any listing business you want quickly, seamlessly and beautifully. Having your listing business in App makes a big different for you and your end-users..

markdownRemark.html:
V1.3

  • Add more 10 awesome brand new design, follow this link https://listpro.now.sh/theme to see how to update it.
  • Migrate to new document https://listpro.now.sh

V1.2

  • Compatible with the CeBuilder - https://inspireui.com
  • Mapping redesign and support search by using Google API - screenshot: https://shrtm.nu/53Iz
  • Integrate with Admob & Facebook Ads

V1.1

  • Ability to create new Listing
  • Support Multi language & Language picker

v1.0

  • Mapping
  • Chat feature: the End user could able to chat with the Listing owner
  • Social Login
  • WP user login
  • My booking with Calendar
  • Firebase integration
  • Flexible Homepage UI config
  • Menetization and Advertising: by Facebook ADs and AdMob
  • Crash report (via Sentry)
  • Nearest locatino on Map
  • Support Rating and Comment
  • New Searching filters
  • Push notification (Firbase or OneSignal)
  • React navigation 2.0 is support
  • Redesign Ling Detail more sexy
  • Chat features is support (via Firebase)
  • Onboarding screen (support Lotties)
  • Control the visibility Booking and Chating feature via Config

Blacklog

  • Claim listing
  • Support payment
  • Please suggest new feature request via our support Github - https://github.com/inspireui/support/issues
